{"word":"θεμόω","slug":"θεμόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n48138\" key=\"qemo/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">θεμόω</orth>, only in phrase [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νῆα] θέμωσε . . χέρσον ἱκέσθαι</foreign> <sense id=\"n48138.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drove</tr_> the ship <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ashore, stranded</tr_> her, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:486\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.486</biblScope> </bibl>; but in ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:542\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">542</biblScope></bibl>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drove</tr_> her landwards, i.e. towards her destination: cf. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">θεμούς·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">διαθέσεις, παραινέσεις</foreign>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author></bibl>, who also has <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">θεμῶν·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">θελήμων</foreign>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}